{"id": "1211173849807331368", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "1185814596448165981", "author_name": "c10h16o_1001", "author_bot": false, "content": "其实我一直疑惑宁菲亚为什么不是深海（。", "timestamp": "2024-02-25T04:52:28.316000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1211173850067505172", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 19, "author_id": "840883092499464222", "author_name": "starry_1018", "author_bot": false, "content": "血肉喚醒體擁有掌控生命能量的能力(菲茵特，羊媽，艾繼絲)或者慾望驅動型(古羅馬3人)", "timestamp": "2024-02-25T04:52:28.378000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1185719465984413801"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1211018373283192932", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1211175552044503100", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 19, "author_id": "387191775183241216", "author_name": "kervin_joshua", "author_bot": false, "content": "有點忘了是孤兒院還是蠟像館有出現幻境然後有說是深海的能力\n孤兒院地下室遇到珊時看到旁邊的蠟像\n有說這像是血肉喚醒體的能力", "timestamp": "2024-02-25T04:59:14.161000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1185814596448165981"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1211173760745340928", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1211177452060024852", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 19, "author_id": "387191775183241216", "author_name": "kervin_joshua", "author_bot": false, "content": "我猜是混沌的優先級最高\n比如說你有血肉的能力但你可以跟其他界域共鳴\n你就會被分到混沌\n而且寧菲亞的能力也沒有特別像深海\n倒是外表還比較像血肉", "timestamp": "2024-02-25T05:06:47.160000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1185814596448165981"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1211173849807331368", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1211186764023201832", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 19, "author_id": "387191775183241216", "author_name": "kervin_joshua", "author_bot": false, "content": "", "timestamp": "2024-02-25T05:43:47.305000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1185814596448165981"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1211186763595259974", "filename": "IMG_3944.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 2538164, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1173463482503536711/1211186763595259974/IMG_3944.png?ex=6a377a13&is=6a362893&hm=10c3890006f0f8d2e2eec237eff65395e04e54c3058b457282a0aca8bbbbac5e&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1211173760745340928", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1211201090658377738", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 19, "author_id": "1185814596448165981", "author_name": "c10h16o_1001", "author_bot": false, "content": "啊这里，不过我当时的理解并不是说深海的特殊能力是幻境和梦境，而是在梦境中看到了属于深海的特殊象征……", "timestamp": "2024-02-25T06:40:43.041000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["387191775183241216"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1211186764023201832", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1211201435354660894", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "1185814596448165981", "author_name": "c10h16o_1001", "author_bot": false, "content": "宁妃主要是感觉她和珊有点像，被海洋所吸引，最后走向海洋结束自己的生命", "timestamp": "2024-02-25T06:42:05.223000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
