{"id": "1211260163881959435", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "848454386598412318", "author_name": "ruko9999", "author_bot": false, "content": ".....等等 這就是傻鯊能直接從觸手轉力量砍\n但是凱刻斯只能讓觸手多拍一下嗎\n太廢了吧凱刻斯", "timestamp": "2024-02-25T10:35:27.195000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "😂", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
